This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a new algorithm for training generative adversarial networks. The paper also involves image generation, which suggests it could also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision). Additionally, the paper involves the use of a guidance network, which could place it in the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper involves the evaluation of the proposed algorithm, which could place it in the sub-category of cs.GR (Graphics).
